        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4vw,2.9rem);letter-spacing:-.035em;line-height:1.06;font-weight:720;max-width:24ch">Eleven sections. Every one gated, none of them decorative.</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:1.3rem;max-width:60ch;color:var(--muted);text-wrap:pretty">A recipe isn't free-form prose — it's a fixed shape a linter enforces: neutrality (<strong style="color:var(--ink)">roles, never your paths or product names</strong>), a <code style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:.85em;background:var(--accent-soft);padding:.1em .4em;border-radius:.35em">Done when:</code> on every build step, and scars that carry symptom, root cause and fix. <a href="what-is-a-recipe.html">The full genre →</a></p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.2rem;margin-top:2.6rem;align-items:start">
          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(230px,1fr));gap:.55rem">
